YALLA: an LL library for Coq
============================

Release Notes
=============

v 1.1
-----

  * generalization of properties of ILL with zero
    (and removal of zero/top parameters)
    - iformulas.v
        remove zero/top parameters
    - ill.v
        generalization of the results
    - nn.v
        modified translation using of zero and plus instead of top and with
    - lambek.v / fmiformulas.v
        simple adaptation

  * new files
    - isubs.v
        substitutions on intuitionistic formulas
    - tl.v
        tensor logic
    - consistency.v
        specific instances of axioms of the library for consistency proof

  * miscellaneous
    - subs.v
        simplified proofs
    - ll_fragments.v
        added cut_XX_admissible
        added mix0_wn_one
        added results around mix02
    - fmformulas.v
        a2a -> a2a_n
    - fmiformulas.v
        i2i -> i2i_n


v 1.0 2017/07/18
-----

 First public release

